<h5 id="subject_1041632">
<a href="?PHPSESSID=608b062285b07a8dd1e4c54d0838ba14&amp;topic=109564.msg1041632#msg1041632" rel="nofollow">Re: GURPS基本集，中文翻译完整版</a>
</h5>
<div class="zh_convert" style="float:right;display:none">
[<a href="javascript:convertToTraditional(document.getElementById('msg_1041632'));undefined;">繁</a>
